data.description: Property is two units according to City of Berkeley There are separate meters for both units ,some Dual utilities There is pre-sale escrow is opened with Bay Area escrow Services  Escrow officer 925-553-7540 . Property is in a Trust being sold by Trustees No Probate No Ct. Confirmation  Property is being sold "as Is" there are limited inspections done . Property has on site caretaker .  there is a use access right of way (see prelim )City of Berkeley has allowed property use in the right of way for 20+years  buyers too satisfy any standing questions with city of Berkeley. seller makes no representations regarding use . property zoned multi residence two units but with joined access .Both units were completely repainted  , ADA ramp inside . two kitchens , see diagram floor plan in pictures , huge lot , access from both Parker and Acton close to Shopping, university, medical, easy Fwy access nearby Bart service , hardwood floors , front unit has new kitchen,bath, and utility floors ,rear unit has new kitchen flooring and large yard for Garden ,amazing possibilities
